    <broman@spawar.navy.mil>.

  * Following two patches are from Vincent Broman.
  * g10/mainproc.c (proc_tree): use iobuf_get_real_fname() in preference
    to iobuf_get_fname().
  * g10/openfile.c (open_sigfile): handle .sign prefixed files correctly.

